name: ends of river
description:
ends of river - river here is defined as a journey of every human being. and the picture of the pillars lined up is interpreted as the belief we have in the Almighty. at the end of the journey, or at the 'ends of the river', whether we have faith in which pillar, we will end up in the same place. a place that higher than where we are now. and perhaps more beautiful than any place we've ever lived in before.
